data.description: Royal Ridge is a 55+ community that's all about activities!  They offer a terrific pool and spa, clubhouse, exercise room, tennis court, dog run area, and community events every week.  This is truly a community where residents feel welcome.  This is the home to own in Royal Ridge as it offers two large bedrooms, a family room, a living room, a dining room, and two full bathrooms.  There's even a stand-alone fireplace that makes the whole home feel cozy.  From the covered patio to the double front doors to the formal dining room, this home has everything you could want, there's even a small storage area/shed in the back to keep your holiday decorations.  The HVAC system is less than one year old!  Royal Ridge is a quiet community with nearby access to shopping, freeways, and the Las Vegas strip. This community is gated for that extra security. Don't miss out on this one!
